fields.name: Coal Minion
fields.description: Coal Minions are a type of Minion that collects Coal. Coal Minions are unlocked at Coal 1 and can be placed on the Player's Island. The Coal Minion collects Coal.

fields.name: Oak Minion
fields.description: Oak Minions are a type of Minion that collects Oak Wood. Oak Minions are unlocked at Oak Wood 1 and can be placed on the Player's Island. The Oak Minion collects Oak Wood.

fields.name: Enchanted Lava Bucket
fields.description: The Enchanted Lava Bucket is a Minion Fuel that increases Minion speed by 25% for unlimited duration. Same as every fuel with unlimited duration, they can be taken from Minions without being consumed.
